# Dependency directories
# vendor/ is INTENTIONALLY tracked since the go-ethereum -> defiweb swap.
# CI builds with -mod=vendor so a compromised upstream cannot affect a
# build that succeeds locally. To refresh: go mod tidy && go mod vendor.
# (If reintroducing module-mode builds, restore "vendor/" here and
# remove the third_party copies.)

